{"tid":355583,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"扑初龍，dxxxxxxx 速入「原味」內衣褲網上熱賣　醫生：隨時有性病","createTime":"2017-08-11T11:44:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-12T15:23:56.000Z","uid":3806,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"26ef878f7cef07ba9521442238f8d32e7a48c9aa","tid":355583,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T11:44:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170811/bkn-20170811130002646-0811_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170811%2Fbkn-20170811130002646-0811_00822_001.html&d=LqU%2Biehar3Y0COcM%2FKLbcJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=53bbf8d9\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170811/bkn-20170811130002646-0811_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170811/photo/bkn-20170811130002646-0811_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170811134505\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170811%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170811130002646-0811_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170811134505&h=d36bd6bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\ninstagram色情歪風不斷，「原味」內衣褲一應俱全！不少年輕女生公然售賣二手內衣褲，並以「原汁原味」作招徠，標榜「有漬」，吸引男士購買。有醫生警告，這些內衣褲含菌量勢超標，嚴重者更有機會沾染性病！<br />\n<br />\n「有冇哥哥想要小妹嘅絲襪？」、「二手底褲着足兩日，包有漬！」社交網絡Instagram湧現二手內衣褲廣告，依圖片所見，女賣家疑親自着上貨物，擺出性感撩人的姿勢，配上極盡挑逗的文字，推銷內衣褲、絲襪、泳衣等，每件價錢由100至300港元不等。<br />\n<br />\n當中有賣家自稱中學生，而且行事非常謹慎，一般只接受郵購。如果想邀約他們當面交收，便需另繳交收費。記者佯裝顧客，以500多元購買一套「有味」內衣連絲襪套裝，成功約得一位自稱「施小姐」的妙齡少女，在港鐵站交收。<br />\n<br />\n「施小姐」跟記者見面時，神情略見緊張，不時左顧右盼，交貨後未收錢即想離去，要記者提醒：「吓你未收錢喎」，才恍然大悟，以笑遮醜，聲稱因為趕時間而心情焦急，並多番推搪記者查詢，着記者事後用WeChat溝通。<br />\n<br />\n記者期後戴上塑料手套，檢查購入的內衣套裝，發現內衣留有疑似人體分泌物，絲襪更附上多條毛髮。皮膚專科醫生陳厚毅接受訪問時表示，這些內衣褲或帶有病菌，有機會沾染性病,"},{"pid":"00aa417cd9e69f395dd17e11546630feead3775c","tid":355583,"uid":105715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T11:46:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63e2788f618c5195971129598104f130cfaeb2d1","tid":355583,"uid":62668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T11:47:25.000Z","msg":"條女好似幾正喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bafede5585561098d238d297508d4242aa5d7f51","tid":355583,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T11:49:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>條女好似幾正喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n記者係朴初襱😍"},{"pid":"e201c9dd7679aa1652e6c2184373682e6cf5bdca","tid":355583,"uid":46500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T11:49:32.000Z","msg":"都要條女有性病先得嫁嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw 記者點處理件野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f51bc75524de991c360f83acd7f8d4467edc538","tid":355583,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T11:50:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都要條女有性病先得嫁嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw 記者點處理件野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n笠頭打飛機"},{"pid":"1f6bd23e7a930e132dca00b9ff775f5d2459716c","tid":355583,"uid":43979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T11:50:31.000Z","msg":"瓏狗買原味黑絲架"},{"pid":"823d553abdc151c15fc4183fca0b4d6c123e096e","tid":355583,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T11:58:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>瓏狗買原味黑絲架</blockquote><br />\n見到佢係地鐵站交收左對"},{"pid":"dd7b8f5d78e319d0d7fe5a87671d662b7e1a86d9","tid":355583,"uid":70195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T12:00:08.000Z","msg":"有冇中環OL賣有味黑絲<br />\npm me <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36bf90d6f510d23963b6a239c268f837d8271108","tid":355583,"uid":134999,"